nvm use 16

yarn hardhat compile

yarn hardhat deploy-zksync --script deploy_Everything_Including_Pools.ts


use output of deploy scripts to verify contracts



Then go to my dapp and fill in information in App.vue and run

yarn serve
or
yarn build



Optional:

yarn hardhat deploy-zksync --script deploy_The_Greeter.ts

to create Greeter contract on mainnet







~~~~~~OOOOOORRRRRR !~~~~~~~

yarn hardhat deploy-zksync --script 1deploy_ZKBTC.ts

Get Auction and zkBTC and Make two Liquidity Pools.
reminder, Make two Liquidity Pools.

Fill in LP Token, LP Token #2, zkBTC, Auction, 0xBitcoin Token address in deploy_Pool_0xBTC_zkBTC.ts and deploy_Pool_ETH.ts

After 


yarn hardhat deploy-zksync --script deployStakingETH.ts

and

yarn hardhat deploy-zksync --script deployStaking0xBTC.ts


THEN fill in the Staking Contract #1 and #2, LP Token #1 and #2, zkBTC, Auction, 0xBitcoin addresses in the dAPPs and ur good to go

edit App.Vue file for this


